Fix learning pipeline: close verification gap, add WindEventPredictor, expand 24/7 collection to all 35 lakes

- WindEventPredictor: predicts frontal passages, north flow, clearing wind, glass windows, pre/post-frontal, thermal cycles
- Verification window expanded from 2hr to 48hr so predictions survive app closure
- Server cron now collects 22 stations across all 35 Utah lakes (was 7 lakes, 13 stations)
- DataCollector dynamically pulls lake list from LAKE_CONFIGS instead of hardcoded arrays
- Learning threshold lowered from 10 to 5 with confidence-scaled weight adjustments
- Discovered patterns now actively used in calculateNewWeights (peak hour, wind type dominance)
- Session feedback collects estimated wind speed for location-specific bias correction
- LearningDashboard shows pattern insights, wind event intelligence, data health metrics
- Fixed pruneOldData index mismatch for ACCURACY/INDICATORS stores
